NAME

    Parse::Syslog::Mail - Parse mailer logs from syslog


DESCRIPTION

   This module offers a simple interface to gather mail information 
   from a syslog file. It uses Parse::Syslog for reading the syslog, 
   and offer the same simple interface. Currently supported log 
   formats are: Sendmail, Postfix, Qmail.


INSTALLATION

    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

    Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the 
    following commands:

        perl Build.PL
        ./Build
        ./Build test
        ./Build install


